+### `app.setUserAgentOverride(options)`
+
+* `options` [AppUserAgentOverrideOptions](structures/app-user-agent-override-options.md)
+
+Sets the global fallback user agent and User-Agent Client Hints metadata. The
+override is used when no user agent override is set at the `session` or
+`webContents` level.
+
+Call this API before creating sessions or windows when the override must apply
+to early navigations, frames, shared workers, service workers, and dedicated
+workers.
+
+### `app.clearUserAgentOverride()`
+
+Clears the global user agent override and restores Electron's default global
+fallback user agent and User-Agent Client Hints metadata.
+
 ### `app.getLocale()`
 
 Returns `string` - The current application locale, fetched using Chromium's `l10n_util` library.
@@ -1817,6 +1834,9 @@ This is the user agent that will be used when no user agent is set at the
