+#### `ses.setUserAgentOverride(options)`
+
+* `options` [SessionUserAgentOverrideOptions](structures/session-user-agent-override-options.md)
+
+Overrides the user agent, User-Agent Client Hints metadata, and optionally
+`acceptLanguages` for this session.
+
+The override applies to navigations and workers created after the call.
+`WebContents` instances can use `webContents.setUserAgentOverride` to override
+the session-wide value for frames and dedicated workers. Shared workers and
+service workers use the session override because they are scoped to the
+session's storage partition.
+
+#### `ses.clearUserAgentOverride()`
+
+Clears this session's user agent and `acceptLanguages` override. Future
+navigations and workers fall back to the app-level override or Electron's
+default user agent metadata.
+
 #### `ses.isPersistent()`
 
 Returns `boolean` - Whether or not this session is a persistent one. The default
